705997f-a.original_title: Brooklyn: New Jersey Avenue - Wortman Avenue
705997f-a.text:
New Jersey Ave., east side, north from Wortman Ave., showing frame homes below street level, and more recently built brick home on the street level.
August 4, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
